Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:32.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after\NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves\N caught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mother-sama!\N--Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Otohime-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust the woman who you chose to be your wife
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty! Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:04:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:15.57,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"A Sudden Tragedy! \NA Gunshot Shuts Down the Future!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime's voyage was to determine\N the fate of the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we were all worrying \Nbut it was nothing compared to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the burden of the Neptune family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole Ryugu Kingdom was restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all we could do was pray\N for the Queen's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A Tamate Box?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Captain. I heard that they \Nhave one at the Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it makes anyone grow older?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance, a small brat like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would become a sexy mature woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Problem solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I can get married to \NShirahoshi right away, I suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go steal that Tamate Box thing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute. There is no way \Nto break in to the Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But if you get married to Shirahoshi first...\N--You can go in and out as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi is not bad-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she grows older by 10 to 20 years,\N she will be really hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she'll get even bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll look just fine! I like big women!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the legendary Mermaid \NPrincess who can control the Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I become her husband\N and seize that power,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our dream will come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the dream of all the ancestors\N of Vander Decken family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll start writing \Nan invitation to our wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to propose to her first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't have any friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There had been no word \Nfrom the Queen for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:18.93,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,WE NEED YOUR SIGNATURE FOR\N THE FUTURE OF THE ISLAND!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And worries kept growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna hear her speeches again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come back safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Boss. Where is Otohime-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will she come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep faith in her and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She embarked on a voyage to make \Nthe future better for you kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, please be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:07:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She will be fine-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's trust in her and wait-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one week felt like 100 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:08:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are so happy just to see you alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a few days of convincing,\N Queen Otohime finally succeeded...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in calming down the Celestial Dragons and \Nshe brought back with her a sheet of paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which held the fate \Nof the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CONCHCORDE PLAZA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, the World Nobles\N are very influential...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the World Summit - the Summit of Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to what they wrote\N on this sheet of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To foster friendship between\N the Fish-Men and humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will pledge our endorsement \Nof their duly signed petition."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means if we can submit a petition\N with many signatures at the Summit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:09:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this one sheet of paper will \Ngive us all the support we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can relocate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The Celestial Dragons will support the petition?\N--I have mixed feelings about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what I need now is more signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is wait for \Nyou to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Express your intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to relocate to the world above and\N live together with the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need your signature!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:10:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You children, you aren't going to go back\N on your pledge after raising my hopes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't! My mom said she will sign too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama, \Nthis small box won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know the \Npopulation of this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, here, here! Put \Nthem in here from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:11:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who support the Queen's passion,\N put your signature in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fish-Men and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were trying to ignore\N the history of racism.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Queen took the first \Nstep herself and now we have hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can get enough signatures, \Nthe future of the island could change for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have helped Arlong if \Nhe could have understood better...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about Queen Otohime's firm belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:12:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Brother Tai were here to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Signatures keep coming\N in from all over the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's going well, isn't it?\N--Yes, it's like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of your courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got encouraged at that very moment,\N that this island would change for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the moment that the Sea Kings\N came and stared at the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi called them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Merfolk can communicate \Nwith fish and talk to them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one can talk to those great Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:13:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even your father Neptune who can talk to whales,\N doesn't know how to talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But according to our royal family's legend,\N once in several hundred years,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one with an ability to communicate\N with the Sea Kings, will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--With those giant Sea Kings?!\N--And Shirahoshi is the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and she will meet someone who will guide\N her and her power in the right direction
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it will cause a major change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's true, there will be a \Nmajor change on this island too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it help what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it could.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a power of love that can save thousands\N of lives if only the bearer wishes to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with the wrong intentions, that power \Ncould sink the whole world into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is one of the most \Nfearsome powers in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi doesn't know that she \Nhas that power and she doesn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how to control it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something were ever to shock her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she could unintentionally \Ndrive the Sea Kings berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fish-Man Island would be flattened\N like a pancake! What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I can take care of it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the three of you will have to \Nbecome strong warriors someday
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and as her brothers and as warriors,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,protect your baby sister with your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes!\N--Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then the unexpected happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signatures were mounting up at a rapid pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The islanders still didn't trust humans
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they were hoping to see \Nthe beginning of a new era.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought our signatures again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's against the rules!\N Each person can only vote once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it means a lot to me that you did so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your efforts finally paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How could the box catch fire?\N--Water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the fire now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The signatures we collected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the fire! We have \Nto save the signatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are very important! I have to save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them burn!\N They are everyone's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the future of the Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save the signatures now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save yourself! \NLeave the rest up to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama has been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shooter must be here somewhere!\N Protect the royal family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mother!\N--Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here! Get on the gondola now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty! Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Your Majesty!\N--Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, Princess, this is pretty serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who're you?!\N--Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stay away from the Princess!\N--Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mother-sama! Mother!\N--Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Who the hell did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Didn't an emergency team arrive yet?!\N--Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be forgiven! I'll make him pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay near me, my angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose your temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My guard was down. Because I was \Nthrilled that everybody was signing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Fukaboshi, I should \Nbe the one who is frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, you need treatment now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it doesn't matter who did this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get angry on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:19:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let resentment or hatred \Nget the better of you for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mother-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi, keep your senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something were ever to shock her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:20:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moonfish mambo! Moonfish mambo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moonfish mambo! Moonfish mambo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moonfish mambo! Moonfish mambo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's fun! It's fun!\N--Shake, shake! Shake, shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's nothing! Let's sing Shirahoshi!\N--Moonfish mambo! Shake, shake, shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We three will always be \Nthere for you-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mambo dance is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun-do-re-mi-fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Princes, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop them!\N--That's not appropriate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, look, we're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will protect our baby sister\N like this forever-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:21:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Can't you see \Nthe Queen's situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will collect the signatures\N that burned away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We three will become great \Nwarriors like our father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and protect Shirahoshi \Nwith our lives as we promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that place under the real sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Otohime's death, Fish-Man \NIsland is consumed by rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.67,0:23:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the end for her ideal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After relating the subsequent \Nevents on Fish-Man Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and finishing his story, Jimbei \Nagain apologizes to Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.76,0:23:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nami's reply was utterly unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Back to the Present! Hordy Makes a Move!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
